Subject: [PATCH v6 3/7] mtd: ubi: block: use notifier to create ubiblock from
 parameter
Message-ID: <c24478ed4f9f985c4e6ff83b66a07fba64fb6812.1702850093.git.daniel@makrotopia.org>
References: <cover.1702850093.git.daniel@makrotopia.org>
Precedence: bulk
